81,1,18345,m,html-keyboard-response,2,30699,0.0-2.0,"Imagine you are in a casino, and you go to a room with four slot machines. On pulling a machine, it yeilds a reward. At any point, some machines may be better than the others, but the amount they give varies. Your aim is to maximize your cumulative reward by the end of this experiment.
Machines are pulled by pressing 'Q', 'P', 'M' or 'Z' on the keyboard. These keys are arranged in the same way on the keyboard as the slot machines are on the screen.
Press any button to see an illustration of the trial screen and the keyboard mapping!","""","""","""","""","""","""","""","""","""","2021-05-06 02:59:17",202.168.85.199,"Mozilla/5.0 (X11
